// 1. Replaced var with the explicit Holder struct in functions Put and Collect
// 2. Added require statements to check for valid inputs in function Collect
// 3. Replaced the external call with transfer in function Collect to prevent reentrancy
// 4. Changed the constructor name to match the contract name
// 5. Changed the way messages are added to the Log to avoid the reentrancy vulnerability